{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "ulpgl-cms-collection-001",
    "name": "ULPGL-Goma — Backend API",
    "description": "Collection complète de l'API backend ULPGL-Goma (Node.js + Express + Sequelize + MariaDB).\n\n**Auth** : JWT Bearer token (récupéré via `/auth/login`)\n\n**Comptes par défaut (seed)** :\n- Super admin : `admin@ulpgl.net` / `Admin@2026`\n- Publieur faculté : `publisher@ulpgl.net` / `Publisher@2026`\n\n**Variables** :\n- `{{base_url}}` : URL du backend (par défaut http://localhost:8001)\n- `{{token}}` : auto-rempli après `Login Admin` ou `Login Publisher`\n- `{{content_id}}`, `{{schedule_id}}`, `{{center_id}}` : auto-remplis lors des créations",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8001", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "content_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "schedule_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "center_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "faculty_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "reset_token", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/health",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/health", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "health"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', data.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token saved');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@ulpgl.net\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@2026\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "description": "Renvoie `{ token, user }`. Le token est automatiquement sauvegardé dans la variable `{{token}}`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Publisher)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', pm.response.json().token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"publisher@ulpgl.net\",\n  \"password\": \"Publisher@2026\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (current user)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register new user (Admin only)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Jane Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"jane@ulpgl.net\",\n  \"password\": \"Jane@2026\",\n  \"role\": \"faculty_publisher\",\n  \"facultyId\": {{faculty_id}}\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register"] },
            "description": "Réservé super_admin. `role` ∈ ['super_admin', 'faculty_publisher']. `facultyId` requis pour publisher."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot password",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data.devLink) {",
                  "  const m = data.devLink.match(/token=([a-f0-9]+)/);",
                  "  if (m) { pm.collectionVariables.set('reset_token', m[1]); console.log('reset_token saved'); }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@ulpgl.net\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/forgot-password", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "forgot-password"] },
            "description": "Renvoie toujours 200 (anti-leak). Si SendGrid n'est pas configuré, un `devLink` est inclus dans la réponse et le `reset_token` est extrait automatiquement."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reset password",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{reset_token}}\",\n  \"password\": \"NewPassword@2026\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/reset-password", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "reset-password"] },
            "description": "Token unique (anti-replay : `usedAt` set après succès). Expiration : 1h."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
